translation.Name: Metro Note [BLUE]
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: Our Lieutenant colonel had gone fishing the other week and threw out his keycard in the trash. Why? I don't know. Maybe it's a form of protest. You see, his old brain hates all this new shiny technology. He keeps going on about how good old keys are better and how life was superior back in the old days, despite him constantly droning on about how the new generation has it all so easy...
